targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  1 AS "value",
  createddate AS "time" 
FROM wuzeln.person pe 
  JOIN wuzeln.player p ON p.person_id = pe.id
  JOIN wuzeln.team t on t.id = p.team_id
  JOIN wuzeln.match m on m.id = t.match_id
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(m.createddate) 
  AND m.enddate is not null
  AND pe.nickname IN ( $nickname )
GROUP BY m.id

SELECT 
now() as time,
  t.color, 
  count(distinct(m.id))
FROM wuzeln.person pe 
  JOIN wuzeln.player p ON p.person_id = pe.id
  JOIN wuzeln.team t on t.id = p.team_id
  JOIN wuzeln.match m on m.id = t.match_id
WHERE m.enddate IS NOT NULL 
  AND t.winner 
  AND $__timeFilter(m.createddate)
  AND pe.nickname IN ( $nickname )
GROUP BY t.color

WITH winner_count as (
SELECT
 count(m.id) AS "value",
  pe.nickname AS nickname
FROM wuzeln.person pe 
  JOIN wuzeln.player p ON p.person_id = pe.id
  JOIN wuzeln.team t on t.id = p.team_id
  JOIN wuzeln.match m on m.id = t.match_id
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(m.createddate) AND
   m.enddate is not null AND
  t.winner = TRUE
GROUP BY pe.nickname
  ), 
all_count as (
SELECT
 count(m.id) AS "value",
  pe.nickname AS nickname
FROM wuzeln.person pe 
  JOIN wuzeln.player p ON p.person_id = pe.id
  JOIN wuzeln.team t on t.id = p.team_id
  JOIN wuzeln.match m on m.id = t.match_id
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(m.createddate) AND
   m.enddate is not null
GROUP BY pe.nickname
  )
  
SELECT wc.value / cast(ac.value as float) as value, 
ac.nickname as metric,
now() as time
FROM winner_count wc 
JOIN all_count ac ON wc.nickname = ac.nickname
AND wc.nickname IN ( $nickname )
ORDER BY value DESC

WITH winner_count as (
SELECT
 count(m.id) AS "value",
  pe.nickname AS nickname
FROM wuzeln.person pe 
  JOIN wuzeln.player p ON p.person_id = pe.id
  JOIN wuzeln.team t on t.id = p.team_id
  JOIN wuzeln.match m on m.id = t.match_id
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(m.createddate) AND
   m.enddate is not null AND
  t.winner = TRUE
GROUP BY pe.nickname
  ), 
all_count as (
SELECT
 count(m.id) AS "value",
  pe.nickname AS nickname
FROM wuzeln.person pe 
  JOIN wuzeln.player p ON p.person_id = pe.id
  JOIN wuzeln.team t on t.id = p.team_id
  JOIN wuzeln.match m on m.id = t.match_id
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(m.createddate) AND
   m.enddate is not null
GROUP BY pe.nickname
  )
  
SELECT 
ac.nickname as name,
(wc.value / cast(ac.value as float))*100 as value,
ac.value as "nr. of played",
wc.value as "nr. of won"
FROM winner_count wc 
JOIN all_count ac ON wc.nickname = ac.nickname
WHERE wc.nickname IN ( $nickname )
ORDER BY value DESC

SELECT 
now() as time,
  g.position, 
  count(*)
FROM wuzeln.goal g
  JOIN wuzeln.player pl ON g.player_id = pl.id 
  JOIN wuzeln.person pe ON pl.person_id = pe.id
WHERE $__timeFilter(g.date) 
  AND pe.nickname IN( $nickname )
GROUP BY g.position

panels.description: Percentage of matches played with Andi  in the same team. Taking into consideration only matches where Andi played.

targets.rawSql:
WITH 
matches_with_andi AS (
SELECT distinct(m.*)
FROM wuzeln.person pe 
JOIN wuzeln.player pl ON pe.id = pl.person_id
JOIN wuzeln.team t ON pl.team_id = t.id
JOIN wuzeln.match m on t.match_id = m.id
WHERE pe.nickname = 'Andi' AND
 $__timeFilter(m.createddate) AND
   m.enddate is not null
),
with_andi AS (
SELECT pe.nickname, count(*) as count
FROM wuzeln.person pe 
JOIN wuzeln.player pl ON pe.id = pl.person_id
JOIN wuzeln.team t ON pl.team_id = t.id
JOIN wuzeln.player pl2 ON pl2.team_id = t.id
JOIN wuzeln.person pe2 ON pl2.person_id = pe2.id
JOIN matches_with_andi m on m.id = t.match_id
WHERE pe2.nickname = 'Andi'
GROUP BY pe.nickname
ORDER BY count desc)

SELECT
wa.nickname as metric, 
TRUNC((cast(wa.count as decimal) / count(*))* 100, 2) as value,
now() as time
FROM with_andi wa
JOIN wuzeln.person pe ON wa.nickname = pe.nickname 
JOIN wuzeln.player pl ON pe.id = pl.person_id
JOIN wuzeln.team t ON pl.team_id = t.id
JOIN matches_with_andi m on m.id = t.match_id
WHERE pe.nickname IN ( $nickname )
GROUP BY wa.nickname, wa.count, pe.nickname
ORDER BY value desc

panels.title: With Andi in Team

targets.rawSql:
WITH 
matches_with_andi AS (
SELECT distinct(m.*)
FROM wuzeln.person pe 
JOIN wuzeln.player pl ON pe.id = pl.person_id
JOIN wuzeln.team t ON pl.team_id = t.id
JOIN wuzeln.match m on t.match_id = m.id
WHERE pe.nickname = 'Andi' AND
 $__timeFilter(m.createddate) AND
   m.enddate is not null
),
with_andi AS (
SELECT pe.nickname, count(*) as count
FROM wuzeln.person pe 
JOIN wuzeln.player pl ON pe.id = pl.person_id
JOIN wuzeln.team t ON pl.team_id = t.id
JOIN wuzeln.player pl2 ON pl2.team_id = t.id
JOIN wuzeln.person pe2 ON pl2.person_id = pe2.id
JOIN matches_with_andi m on m.id = t.match_id
WHERE pe2.nickname = 'Andi'
GROUP BY pe.nickname
ORDER BY count desc)

SELECT
wa.nickname as metric, 
TRUNC((cast(wa.count as decimal) / count(*))* 100, 2) as value,
wa.count as with_andi, count(*) as all_played
FROM with_andi wa
JOIN wuzeln.person pe ON wa.nickname = pe.nickname 
JOIN wuzeln.player pl ON pe.id = pl.person_id
JOIN wuzeln.team t ON pl.team_id = t.id
JOIN matches_with_andi m on m.id = t.match_id
WHERE pe.nickname IN ( $nickname )
GROUP BY wa.nickname, wa.count, pe.nickname
ORDER BY value desc

SELECT
  avg(sp.scoreoffensive),
  date_trunc('month', m.createddate) as "time",
  pe.nickname as metric
FROM
  wuzeln.stats_player sp 
  JOIN wuzeln.player p on sp.player_id = p.id 
  JOIN wuzeln.team t on t.id = p.team_id
  JOIN wuzeln.match m on m.id = t.match_id
  JOIN wuzeln.person pe ON p.person_id = pe.id
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(m.createddate)
  AND pe.nickname IN ( $nickname )
GROUP BY pe.nickname, time
ORDER BY pe.nickname, time

panels.description:
Score is computed as: looser_goals / winner_goals.
Quality is normalized to: min=0, max=0.9

targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
m.method as method , 
avg( ((cast(sm.looserscore as double precision )/ sm.winnerscore)/0.9)*100) as "avg quality",
avg( cast(sm.looserscore as double precision )/ sm.winnerscore) as "avg score",
count(m) as matches
FROM wuzeln.stats_match sm
JOIN wuzeln.match m ON m.id = sm.match_id
WHERE $__timeFilter(m.createddate)
GROUP BY method

panels.title: Match Quality

targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
m.method as metric , 
avg( ((cast(sm.looserscore as double precision )/ sm.winnerscore)/0.9)*100) as value,
 date_trunc('month', m.createddate) as time
FROM wuzeln.stats_match sm
JOIN wuzeln.match m ON m.id = sm.match_id
WHERE $__timeFilter(m.createddate)
GROUP BY metric, time
ORDER BY time

SELECT 
(m.method || '_COUNT') as metric , 
count(m) as value,
 date_trunc('month', m.createddate) as time
FROM wuzeln.stats_match sm
JOIN wuzeln.match m ON m.id = sm.match_id
WHERE $__timeFilter(m.createddate)
GROUP BY metric, time
ORDER BY time

SELECT 
m.method as metric , 
avg( ((cast(sm.looserscore as double precision )/ sm.winnerscore)/0.9)*100) as value,
now() as time
FROM wuzeln.stats_match sm
JOIN wuzeln.match m ON m.id = sm.match_id
GROUP BY metric

WHERE

  AND pe.nickname IN ( $nickname )

select DISTINCT
EXTRACT(epoch FROM m.enddate - m.startdate)/60,
m.startdate as "time"
from wuzeln.player p 
  JOIN wuzeln.team t on t.id = p.team_id
  JOIN wuzeln.match m on m.id = t.match_id
  JOIN wuzeln.person pe ON p.person_id = pe.id
where m.enddate is not null 
AND $__timeFilter(m.startdate)
AND pe.nickname IN ( $nickname )
